channel.title: [R]Agile Gnome (Advanced gnome agility)
channel.description:
[b]Original post: http://villavu.com/forum/showthread.php?t=66413[/b]
I'm not in the best of moods right now so I'll just edit this post later to make it look cool. I'm kinda just burned out at the moment so I'll list the base features of the script:
[*] Runs the advanced gnome agility course [*] Eats food if you're below 60% [*] Guaranteed 50k+ exp/hour no matter what level [*] Break system, failsafes, SRL Stats, you know, all the stuff I usually add to scripts
Also don't let the [R] fool you, it does run on R2 of course, but because R1 just got buried in it's grave, R2 = Reflection, period.
Please visit the original post (at the top of this post) for the script.
